Narito ang aking palagay.

254
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,919
Wala na ang asawa ni Dezhao.

255
00:14:50,519 --> 00:14:51,720
Isang balo na tulad niya,

256
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,879
