292
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:52,519
Ang hangal kong anak.

293
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:54,080
Pumunta ka at gumawa ng isang utusan.

294
00:15:54,519 --> 00:15:55,360
Sabihin mo lang,

295
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:56,879
