297
00:15:58,559 --> 00:15:59,120
Oo.

298
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,679
Bale wala.

299
00:16:00,879 --> 00:16:01,639
Ako na lang ang pupunta.

300
00:16:10,519 --> 00:16:12,279
[Kung gayon, simulan mo itong pag-isipan simula ngayon.]

301
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,080
