313
00:16:54,679 --> 00:16:55,240
Gu Jinzhao,

314
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,200
Ano nga ba talaga ang sinusubukan mong gawin?

315
00:16:57,399 --> 00:16:58,759
Wala naman akong sinusubukang gawin.

316
00:17:00,519 --> 00:17:02,120
