Ano ang ibig sabihin niyan?

322
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,440
At kailan ang 'balang araw'?

323
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,960
Wala ka bang planong magpakasal?

324
00:17:20,279 --> 00:17:21,599
Hindi ko naman talaga plinano ang magpakasal.

325
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:22,279
Kalokohan.

326
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,839
Ano ang ginagawa mo?

327
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:26,880
-Tinakot mo ako.
-Tinakot mo ako.

328
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,759
Hindi ako sang-ayon.

329
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:33,720
Hindi pa kasama si lola,

330
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:34,880
Ako ang unang hindi sumang-ayon.

331
00:17:35,119 --> 00:17:36,200
Anong karapatan mong hindi sumang-ayon?

332
00:17:36,319 --> 00:17:37,039
May karapatan ako—

333
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:43,920
Alam ko.

334
00:17:44,599 --> 00:17:45,880
Dahil sa nangyari sa iyong ina,

335
00:17:46,839 --> 00:17:48,240
