336
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:49,839
Pero...

337
00:17:50,079 --> 00:17:51,519
Pero parang pagnenegosyo lang ito.

338
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,400
Maraming tao ang nawawalan ng buong puhunan nila.

339
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,559
Hindi ibig sabihin na dapat na lang sumuko ang lahat.

340
00:17:59,279 --> 00:17:59,880
Hindi mo naiintindihan.

341
