345
00:18:14,359 --> 00:18:15,599
Hindi ako nagsasalita ng kalokohan.

346
00:18:16,119 --> 00:18:17,000
Lola,

347
00:18:17,119 --> 00:18:17,799
hindi ba siya umaasa rin na

348
