371
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:06,279
May sasabihin siya sa iyo.

372
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:09,160
Oo.

373
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,440
Jinzhao,

374
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,759
Malapit nang matapos ang panahon ng pagluluksa.

375
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,640
Kailan mo planong bumalik sa kabisera?

376
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,680
Hindi ko pa naisip 'yan.

377
00:19:25,039 --> 00:19:25,680
Ano?

378
00:19:26,799 --> 00:19:27,559
Tiya,

379
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:29,160
