380
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,079
Paano ako maglalakas-loob?

381
00:19:33,359 --> 00:19:35,440
Kahit hindi ka miyembro ng aming pamilya,

382
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,960
Ikaw ang paboritong anak ng matandang babae.

383
00:19:38,759 --> 00:19:40,920
Paano ko nagawang tumanggi na manatili ka?

384
00:19:47,519 --> 00:19:48,160
Binibini,

385
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,759
bakit siya nagsasalita

386
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:51,039
