419
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,519
Huwag ka ring magmadaling makipagkumpitensya.

420
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:00,920
Ibenta sa kahit anong presyo

421
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:01,960
