429
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:21,839
Suriing mabuti ang lahat.

430
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:24,920
Tara na, binibini.

431
00:21:28,759 --> 00:21:29,319
Binibini

432
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:30,720
Ginoong Chen.

433
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:43,799
Bakit siya nandito?

434
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:52,440
Ginoong Chen.

435
00:21:53,279 --> 00:21:54,000
Gu Jinzhao,

436
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,160
