440
00:22:04,880 --> 00:22:05,359
Ako...

441
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:06,759
Talaga...

442
00:22:07,279 --> 00:22:08,759
Hindi talaga dapat kita pinagbigyan.

443
00:22:09,039 --> 00:22:10,279
Umalis ka na lang nang walang pasabi,

444
00:22:10,279 --> 00:22:11,640
