480
00:24:38,799 --> 00:24:39,359
Ikaw

481
00:24:40,359 --> 00:24:41,279
Ikaw... manahimik ka.

482
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,559
Pag-usapan natin ito nang mahinahon.

483
00:24:46,799 --> 00:24:47,440
Sige.

484
00:24:49,799 --> 00:24:51,640
Ang sinabi ko sa iyo sa Templo ng Baoxiang,

485
00:24:52,599 --> 00:24:53,359
