487
00:24:55,799 --> 00:24:56,640
Aling bahagi?

488
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,519
Tungkol sa pagsasaalang-alang sa akin.

489
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:03,319
Hindi ba't sinabi ko na sa'yo?

490
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:04,759
Hindi ko ito isinasaalang-alang.

491
00:25:07,039 --> 00:25:08,279
Gu Jinzhao.

492
00:25:10,519 --> 00:25:11,640
Sa pag-uugali mo nang ganito,

493
00:25:11,799 --> 00:25:13,319
Inaasahan mo bang kakausapin kita nang mahinahon?

494
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:14,359
Sumama ka sa akin pabalik sa kabisera.

495
00:25:17,359 --> 00:25:19,000
Siguro'y nasa tabi mo lang ako,

496
00:25:19,519 --> 00:25:20,880
